content:
Because in that dark space,
there were only things that looked like Lumia, {短暂停}
I think.

Lately I've been hearing Neighbors talk about their dreams,
I wonder if you ever discuss yours with others, {短暂停}
I've never told anyone about mine, not even my father.

Because someone told me in a dream... (thinking) {短暂停}
Let's talk about it next time,
I need to figure out how to describe it properly.

Well,{短暂停}
I usually don't judge my clients,
but I've met some real Kaijin before.

In other words, after the client's father passed away,
for some reason,
his remaining vitality transformed the box into something supernatural.
